@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Module 1: The Basics";
}

<!-- Title -->
<div class="container">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col text-center">
            <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
            <p>Welcome to Module 1: The Basics. In this module, you will learn the fundamentals of sign language, which will include the alphabet and simple words.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Introduction -->
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col">
            <h2>Introduction</h2>
            <p>Sign language is a visual language that uses hand shapes, facial expressions, and body movements to communicate. Learning the basics is the first step to becoming proficient in sign language.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Lessons -->
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h3>Lession 1: The Alphabet</h3>
            <p>Start by learning the sign language alphabet. Each letter has a unique hand shape.</p>
            <img src="~/images/alpahbet-chart.jpg" alt="Sign Language Alphabet Chart" class="img-fluid" />
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h3>Lession 2: Simple Words</h3>
            <p>Once you are comfortable with the alpahbet, move on to simple words like "hello", "thank you", and "please".</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Hello</strong>: <img src="~/images/hello.jpg" alt="Hello" class="img-fluid" /></li>
                <li><strong>Thank you</strong>: <img src="~/images/thank-you.jpg" alt="Thank you" class="img-fluid" /></li>
                <li><strong>Please</strong>: <img src="~/images/please.jpg" alt="Please" class="img-fluid" /></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Videos -->
    <div class="row mt-4">
        <div class="col">
            <h2>Instructional Videos</h2>
            <p>Watch these videos to see the signs in action and practice along.</p>
            <div class="embed-responsive embed-responsive-16by9 mb-4">
                <iframe class="embed-responsive-item" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/examplevideo1" allowfullscreen></iframe>
            </div>
            <div class="embed-responsive embed-responsive-16by9 mb-4">
                <iframe class="embed-responsive-item" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/examplevideo2" allowfullscreen></iframe>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Practice Activities -->
    <div class="row mt-4">
        <div class="col">
            <h2>Practice Activities</h2>
            <p>Practice what you have learned with these activities.</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Spell your name using the sign language alphabet.</li>
                <li>Practice signing "hello" and "thank you" in front of a mirror.</li>
                <li>Quiz yourself on the alphabet with flashcards.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>